{"tid":2310200,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"關於走佬，請大家幫助應走先既人解鎖","createTime":"2020-12-03T05:49:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T13:38:43.000Z","uid":53673,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"be8a442259b6efbc1aaa8b489e7d1a5d514cade8","tid":2310200,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T05:49:34.000Z","msg":"由於香港已淪陷，冇險可守<br />\n而家最應該走既係有名有姓公眾人物或者比狗/左報搞過既人<br />\n但由於呢班人部份覺得走佬有負香港人<br />\n心理上有「齊上齊落」既道德枷鎖<br />\n所以死都唔會走<br />\n希望大家用民意幫呢班人解開佢既道德枷鎖<br />\n說服佢地暫時退居外地<br />\n留得青山在，哪怕冇柴燒<br />\n尤其本身有民意授權既議員<br />\n希望當區選民幫手游說<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7656ed78cb783f81ea41dc677476145a054abe95","tid":2310200,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T06:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16248c9a3e1694181be9f6a6c74eba28b1b4af86","tid":2310200,"uid":146030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T07:00:52.000Z","msg":"希望啱啱總辭同初選勝出嗰班全體流亡"},{"pid":"78e33b1ad723f60e662a186f5d8ca171c0c875cb","tid":2310200,"uid":53673,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T07:05:49.000Z","msg":"岑敖暉fb琴晚話比狗跟, 當區選民快D做野幫佢解鎖啦!!!!!!!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"f7ed8499dc03908a8a3a16697d93453d5fae7f15","tid":2310200,"uid":282855,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T07:08:34.000Z","msg":"大把走撚左啦"},{"pid":"6a3aa9bda3b2d4c799797a2720cb24dfa0dc313f","tid":2310200,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7ed8499dc03908a8a3a16697d93453d5fae7f15","tid":2310200,"uid":282855,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T07:08:34.000Z","m